                <h3 class="subheading">Features and Technology: The Intelligent Electric Cockpit</h3>
                <p>The BE 6 Formula E Edition is thoroughly modern, packing a comprehensive suite of features and integrated technology designed for comfort, connectivity, and safety, all powered by Mahindra’s advanced AdrenoX AI interface and MAIA, the "fastest automotive mind in the world."</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">A. Infotainment and Connectivity</span></p>
                <p>The vehicle’s digital interface is dominated by a stunning, cohesive display setup:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Twin 12.3-inch Screens:</span> The dashboard features dual screens—one for the digital driver's display (instrument cluster) and one for the curved infotainment touchscreen—creating a seamless, high-definition digital cockpit experience.</li>
