                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Storage and Charging: </span>Features like a wireless phone charger, multiple charging ports including a powerful 65W Type-C fast charger, and ample storage solutions cater to the needs of the connected generation.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Premium Touches: </span>Auto-dimming IRVM (Inside Rear View Mirror), auto headlamps, rain-sensing wipers, and high-quality laminated door glass for enhanced noise reduction all contribute to a refined driving atmosphere.</li>
